No. 09-1327. Missouri, Petitioner v. Mark Anthony Gill. 562 U.S. 946, 131 S. Ct. 83,

178 L. Ed. 2d 241,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7684. October 4, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Missouri denied.

Same case below, 300 S.W.3d 225.
